title: The Art of Owning Your Life ft. Ryan Michler, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO217
itunes:title: The Art of Owning Your Life ft. Ryan Michler, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO217
description: My buddy Ryan Michler from Order of Man joins me in the studio and we get riffing on topics like accepting responsibility, mastering skills, and taking back control of your life, whether it's in the area of career or relationships or whatever. There’s a plague of victim mindset running through our culture and it has to be stopped. If you're infected by it, I can’t stop it for you. You have to do it yourself and in this episode we tell you how.
